**Image Generation Prompt (EN)**

Warm late-afternoon light floods a lush tropical courtyard in a small Franconian town. Terracotta and turquoise bistro chairs surround wooden tables set with drinks — a dark rum punch in a tall glass, condensation on the rim. Bird-of-paradise flowers (Strelitzia) and broad palm leaves frame the scene; a small stone pond reflects the golden hour glow. The surrounding walls are warm sandstone with white shutters; colourful paintings hang between climbing plants. A few guests sit relaxed, mid-conversation — no posed smiles, just genuine ease. Soft string lights are just starting to glow overhead. Atmosphere: unhurried, warm, a little lush — like a holiday that didn't require a flight. Photorealistic, shallow depth of field, golden-hour colour grading (amber, deep green, soft coral), no text overlays, no stock-photo stiffness.

